data.title: Forrest Tucker Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Forrest Tucker on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Forrest Tucker including Auntie Mame, Sands of Iwo Jima, and more.
data.text:
Blueprint for Murder

The city foots the bill to dig up a huge building pylon in search of a missing body. Forrest Tucker, Janis Paige and Patrick O'Neal guest star.

It's a Dog's Life

Jessica is visiting her cousin at Langley Manor, a country estate in the South. When he gets killed during a hunt and under the strangest circumstances, Jessica tires to find out what really happened.

Founder's Day

With a Founder's Day event approaching for Walnut Grove, everyone prepares for a celebration complete with games and heated competition. Everyone in the Ingalls family ends up participating, most notably Charles, who meets an unlikely nemesis in the log-splitting competition.

Double Entry

A businessman arouses suspicion when he seems to have more than a business interest in the gold shipments of a stagecoach line.
